Text:
This release is not a MapSource version and not a gmapsupp.img.

Just the worst case scenario - it's a manual recreated installation done with gMapTool and cGPSmapper. This means that search functionality is lost and the preview map in MapSource is created with strange zoom levels.

Stort tack för denna.
Funkar helt perfekt på både min Oregon 550 och på Nuvin.

Det gör alla kartorna i Version2 serien. Vilken jäkla skillnad mot den gamla friluftskratan.
